descriptionHtml:
Quite sometime ago I posted a video on YouTube which explains how to make a working Nordic Puzzle Door. Since then I have been getting several replies and questions.
With this file I have included an .esm which you can place into your DATA folder. You can then open your CK and inspect the cell I created with all the pieces laid out and correctly linked and ready to go. 
I have also included a READ ME file which lists all the pieces you will need as well as a link to my tutorial on YouTube. Or you can just watch it here.
Since I made the video I have learned a lot more about these doors, so some of the stuff I say may seem a bit obsolete. 
I do not explain how all this is done in writing on the READ ME. Sorry, but there is just too much to write out.
author: Zyris
